    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>medium egg noodles</strong> to a pot and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 2-3 min or until almost cooked</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
