      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the noodles are cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> ginger & garlic paste </strong>and <strong>diced chicken thigh</strong>, then cook for 4-5 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
