    {
      "instruction": "<p>When the noodles are almost cooked, add your <strong>halved Tenderstem broccoli</strong> and cook for 2 min further or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain the noodles & Tenderstem broccoli and reserve a cup of the <strong>starchy noodle water</strong></p>",
