    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>cornflour</strong> to a bowl with 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span><strong> cold water</strong> and stir to dissolve</p><p>Add your <strong>sriracha</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>tomato ketchup</strong></p><p>Add 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> vegetable oil</strong> with a splash of the<strong> reserved starchy noodle water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>chilli sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
