    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, add the <strong>drained noodles & Tenderstem broccoli</strong>,<strong> chilli sauce</strong> and <strong>cashew nuts</strong> and stir it all together – these are your<strong> chilli chicken cashew noodles</strong></p><p>Tip: Add another splash of the starchy noodle water if it's looking a little dry</p>",
